Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過作為回報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晨練就算稍微來一會也好 妳一定要參加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早安 我是黑衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們來接我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有由宇同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…剛才阿姨她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的喔 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有戴那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我也給由宇同學拿了一個來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真綯的那個成對的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉雖然看起來很精神 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 稍微安靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35}【珂拉琪（Collage）】\N珂拉琪(Collage)為一種使用膠或漿糊把實物貼\N在畫面上的特殊技法，並有其獨自的繪畫意義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把喜歡的素材按照自己的喜好剪貼起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 黃泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.08,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 黃泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊 妳在做什麼啊 快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:10.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉 黃泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快把剪刀給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說最後家長來了把她帶回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 真的好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的眼睛真的不正常了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本就是那種感覺的人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.75,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了別說了別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉壞掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是心已經死了的意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手了 妳打了篝吧 好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小沙耶老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小鳥遊變成那種樣子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦 只是給了她一點建議而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微痛一會而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷的心靈會提高治癒能力進行再生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得不會再次受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容的橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清風的粉紅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚水的蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色彩漸漸混合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀的顏色變得渾濁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久 翅膀變得一片漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從空中墜落的小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜落 一直墜落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是心已經死了的意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…心已經死了的意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩去了哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…可是…會死的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為…以為自己掉下去的小鳥睜開了眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥的翅膀重新變得潔白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥又飛向了新的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的 應該是更加快樂 更加幸福的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥唱起了歌 小鳥結了婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥考了一百分 小鳥看了有趣的電視節目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這個時候的主角已經有了一種接受死亡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小沙耶老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝一杯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實挺討厭咖啡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不加很多牛奶做成歐蕾咖啡的話就只是泥水而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是啊 咖啡有各種方便之處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小沙耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想救小鳥遊同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 拯救？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救什麼的我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我想救黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼妳為她去死就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 黑衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去美術室看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到很有趣的東西喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我不在這裡殺掉妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣溫柔的小沙耶老師為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美術室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是小鳥遊同學的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話 能不能把那幅畫拿去給小鳥遊同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在這裡也總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我讓黃泉壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這裡有點滲血了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 經理人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了 受傷了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇請假了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…經理人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理人？我們社團不是只有我一個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡幡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩 那個…由宇她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇？那是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？但…但是合宿的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？妳是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我要花很長時間才能記住一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 有那麼一回事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 黑衣她沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看 那個什麼來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像和一年級那個發瘋的學生關係很好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家居然不知道由宇…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行啦 由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼稚園的時候 不喜歡乖乖坐在座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是馬上就會跑去哪裡的由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學時候的海邊夏令營也是一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招 臭真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼從來都不覺得不可思議？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻無法清晰的回憶起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連由宇的家也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去玩過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 我去玩過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想救黃泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿的時候 我跟真綯說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是自己的另一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟自己的苦惱戰鬥的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真實存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…並不是毫無關係的別人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在另一個地方的…另一個自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊 由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個自己總是在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負著我們的苦惱和混亂不堪的思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 通過那些戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過另一個自己的死亡而消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過另一個自己懷抱著苦惱而死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓自己從混亂和迷茫中解放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡前輩也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝同學也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過割斷最執著的思緒 得到了自由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在另一個地方 另一個小鳥遊死掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊就能割斷現在所懷抱的苦惱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉？割斷？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概小鳥遊苦惱的最中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是真綯妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要那個世界的另一個自己死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊…妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能殺死對妳的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣太奇怪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不明白由宇妳說的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 所謂苦惱…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能通過誰死掉或者殺掉誰之類的辦法來解決啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真談心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的把互相所想的事情傾吐出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不通過那樣來解決的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠別人那種事 絕對太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說這種話很不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我一直都把妳當成重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在遇到真綯之前都沒有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會助真綯妳一臂之力的 無論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯 妳想救小鳥遊對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真談心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傾吐互相的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不依靠他人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想那樣做對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠自己來解決可是很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會非常辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受由我們所承受的傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直面傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有這個覺悟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是由宇嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想救黃泉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳對黃泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想救黃泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我別無他法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black★Rock Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:21.41,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:28.82,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰かのようになりたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:28.82,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想要變得和某人一樣堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:32.79,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけどなれるはずもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:32.79,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻又明白無法實現這個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:37.59,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いじけるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:37.59,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如果為此垂頭喪氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:44.85,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心の中にいるもう一人の自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:44.85,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}存在於心中的另一個自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:50.32,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}教えてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:50.32,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}會告訴我答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:58.40,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あるがままなんかじゃきっといられないから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:58.40,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一成不變畏縮不前的話一定會被淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:05.13,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰もがみんな悩んでもがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:05.13,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無論是誰 大家都背負著苦惱而掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:12.22,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}弱音吐いたり 愚痴ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:12.22,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}偶爾示弱 偶爾牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:19.18,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そうやって毎日を過ごしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:19.18,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就像這樣度過了每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.68,0:22:25.94,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}傷つけられることに慣れた僕らは知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.68,0:22:25.94,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終於習慣受傷的我們已然知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:32.77,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}優しさとか思いだけじゃ生きて行けないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:32.77,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只靠溫柔的願望無法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:39.13,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけど自分らしくありたいと思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:39.13,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但是希望可以保持自我的本色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:47.50,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつだって 僕ら歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:47.50,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無論何時 我們都會一路前行